--- yaml ----------------------------------------------------------------------

id:             top
title:          STARK(Â»)

--- jade ----------------------------------------------------------------------

div( class= [ CLASSNAME, "full-width" ])

    h1#main-title
        img( src= "static/logo.png", alt= "Stark" )

        | A <em>straightforward</em> way to build<br>single-page apps and static websites

    .three-features

        div
            h3  Expressive
            p   Yaml, Jade, Stylus used by default. You can even use LiveScript if you want.
        div
            h3  Simple
            p   Everything is a multi-part component: pages, widgets, themes, libraries, configuration. It simply works.
        div
            h3  Plugged-in
            p   Stark strives to reuse what exists. React and Bower components work today. Expect more in the future.


--- styl ----------------------------------------------------------------------

{SELECTOR}

    $logoWidth =            180px
    $logoHeight =           60px

    > h1#main-title

        margin-bottom       0.6 * $logoHeight
        line-height         0.5 * $logoHeight
        font-size           0.4 * $logoHeight
        font-weight         normal
        color               $black

        > img

            float           left
            margin-right    1.5 * $logoHeight


    > .three-features

        > div
            
            float           left
            width           $logoWidth + $logoHeight
            margin-right    0.5 * $logoHeight
            margin-bottom   $lineHeight

            > p

                margin-bottom   0
